concerns.title: Critical Maintainability Issues
concerns.description: MI below 20 indicates code that is harder to understand and modify. Consider simplifying logic or breaking into smaller functions.

concerns.title: Low Maintainability
concerns.description: Low scores driven by long functions (avg 227 lines), high complexity (avg CC: 41.0) and dense code with many operators/operands. Break into smaller, focused functions to improve readability.
